      <link>http://fink.sourceforge.net/news/#2005-11-16%20XCode%202.2%20(10.4%20only).</link>
      <guid>http://fink.sourceforge.net/news/#2005-11-16%20XCode%202.2%20(10.4%20only).</guid>
      <description>
      <p>
The Fink team has had reports of some build problems with the XCode 2.2 compilers.  Until these are sorted out, we recommend that users hold off on upgrading XCode.
